#: serverguide/C/network-auth.xml:1179(para)
msgid ""
"Packt's <ulink url=\"http://www.packtpub.com/OpenLDAP-Developers-Server-Open-"
"Source-Linux/book\">Mastering OpenLDAP</ulink> is a great reference covering "
